attributes.description: Roto Pumps Ltd was incorporated in 1968. Roto Pumps is the pioneer manufacturer of Progressive Cavity Pumps in India, renowned for providing efficient and reliable pumping solutions to a diverse range of industries including Wastewater, Sugar, Paper, Paint, Oil & Gas, Chemicals & Process, Ceramics, Food & Beverages, Renewable Energy & Power, Mining & Explosives, Marine & Defense. The co. is successfully exporting to more than 50 countries. Head office is in Noida, Uttar Pradesh.[1] [2]
